{"tid":584009,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【能人所不能】 支那客大牛市炒英皇樓輸錢  坐艇七年 慘蝕158萬","createTime":"2018-03-07T13:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T06:51:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f755e55fbc3c81aacbbbe6399a9a94020eb7457d","tid":584009,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T13:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180307/large/1520415642_d49f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180307%2Flarge%2F1520415642_d49f.jpg&h=81fa7f99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然樓價不斷急升，但買樓唔一定賺錢，由英皇國際（163）發展入伙近6年的西灣河成安街18號單幢盤港島東18，二手市場再現蝕讓。<br />\n<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，港島東18高層C室，實用面積531方呎，兩房間隔，剛以850萬元成交，呎價16,008元。原業主疑為支那客，2011年5月向英皇以963.1萬元買入單位，持有物業近7年沽貨，賬面已蝕113萬元，若計及釐印費及佣金等開支，料損手約158萬元。<br />\n<br />\n據中原地產成交紀錄顯示，港島東18過去錄得約22宗二手成交，其中10宗蝕讓，業主輸錢比例為45%。港島東18因定價過早，2015年曾劈價兩成促銷，引致早期入市的業主坐艇接近7年。"},{"pid":"80ba9e3cd7e53e9fd3928fa3afecd0f0435f1253","tid":584009,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T13:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買樓一定賺"},{"pid":"9b1e8ec484fd710a31d225bd3784f29c1d9a5ded","tid":584009,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80ba9e3cd7e53e9fd3928fa3afecd0f0435f1253","tid":584009,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T13:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買樓一定賺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T17:10:56.000Z","msg":